text: Montgomery County of the U.S. state of Maryland is north of Washington, D.C. and southwest of Baltimore. It is one of the richest counties in the United States,https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp- dyn/content/article/2006/08/29/AR2006082901543.html and has one of the highest percentages (32.8%) of residents over 25 years old who hold a post-graduate degree. The county seat and largest municipality is Rockville. ==References== Category:Maryland counties Category:1776 establishments in the United States Category:1770s establishments in Maryland
title: Montgomery County, Maryland
